msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The [2019 World Press Freedom Index](https://rsf.org/en/2019-world-press-"
"freedom-index-cycle-fear) compiled by Reporters Without Borders (RSF) shows "
"how hatred of journalists has degenerated into violence, contributing to an "
"increase in fear. The number of countries regarded as safe, where "
"journalists can work in complete security, continues to decline, while "
"authoritarian regimes continue to tighten their grip on the media."
msgstr ""
